with one billion pa</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">ge views.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">A new method of monitoring the international brand position of Global News was established.  It looked at attributes such as trust and objectivity - the BBC is ahead of all competitors on all attributes globally, and most closely associated with </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">trust, high quality</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">and being unbiased and objective.  </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">  </span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">There was</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> comprehensive coverage of </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">the major news</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> stories </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">of the year </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">including the Syria chemical attack, unrest in Mali, demonstrations in Turkey and Brazil, elections in Egypt, Iran, Pakistan an</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">d Zimbabwe, and the hostage incident in Kenya  with greater </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">editorial </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">collaboration across BBC Global News</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> and UK News</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">.  BBC WS language service experts were incre