e growth to 14m globally</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">The strongest growth c</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">ame</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> from Indonesia</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">n, followed by Hausa </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">then Hindi, Mundo, Russian, Turkish and Persian</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">, the majority </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">of which was</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> driven by partnerships</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="background-color:#ffffff; margin:0pt 0pt 13.5pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">The BBC’s global TV and digital operations, BBC World News and bbc.com/news, were brought together to form </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">t</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">he new business entity GN</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> Ltd</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> in order to drive bigger audiences</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> and greater multimedia working</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">GN Ltd. </span><span sty