mily:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">3)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Trust and </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">q</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">uality measurements</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">A new assessment of the global BBC brand shows that </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">the BBC is ahead of all </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">competitors on all attributes globally, and most closely associated with trust, high quality</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">and being unbiased and objective. </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> Where the BBC was less strong – on engagement – efforts have been made to increase regular usage and loyalty amongst the global </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">audience.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">The ‘Brand Tracker’ was</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> established this year to monitor the international brand position of Global News. </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Research </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">was</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> conducted in ten markets, and </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">r</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">esults so far show that the BBC and CNN are clear leaders with the BBC slightly ahead, with bo</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">th gaining significantly higher levels of awareness and consideration than the competition. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Performance varies considerably by market, w</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">hilst</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> CNN </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">i</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">s </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">the BBC’s</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> closest competitor globally, both Al Jazeera English and Euronews having a strong presence in t</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">heir respective primary markets. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">In terms of brand attributes, the BBC is ahead of all competitors on all attributes globally, and most closely associated with trust, high quality</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">and being unbiased and objective. There are also indications that the BBC </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">gains greater social currency and impact</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">from its coverage than key competitors. However, </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">the tracker showed that </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">the BBC </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">was </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">not as strong</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> on </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">attributes such as </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">being passionate</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">and</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> dynamic</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">– </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">this is being addressed through </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">‘Live the Story’, the World New</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">s, World Service and bbc.com/news </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">marketing campaign </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">launched to improve the brand image of global news output.  The campaign emphasises that bringing stories to life in an engaging fashion is a key editorial priority for Global News, and new tools and gui</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">delines </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">to facilitate this </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">were made available </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">to staff </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">across the division.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">4)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Editorial highlights</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">This year saw </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">all editorial elements of </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Global News </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">- World Service, World News and bbc.com/news </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">- </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">become more </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">united than ever before when they came </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">together</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> under one roof in New Broadcasting House. This launched the concept of ‘The World’s Newsroom’, enabling editorial collaboration across the news group, both within Global News and between Global News and UK News.  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">WS Languages, BBC Monitoring and</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> Newsgathering worked closely together to ensure that audiences were able to access the latest information and analysis. </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Some of the highlights included:</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margi